{"tid":1201994,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"新盤部署：御半山II期開放式戶入場費439萬元","createTime":"2019-06-11T07:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T07:26:02.000Z","uid":221051,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"e86bbf57fe8bfde436fae2faec71305c259be6d2","tid":1201994,"uid":221051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"新一輪大盤開售潮揭開序幕。新鴻基地產(00016)旗下屯門御半山II期公布開價，新地代理業務部總經理張卓秀敏表示，首張價單推出108伙，面積由250至531方呎，折實售價439.17萬港元起，折實平均呎價15,166元。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，是次開價與去年1期屬原價，形容為心動價，加推具加價空間。本周六起開放示範單位及收票，最快下周開售。而首批單位中，折實售價500萬元以下共7伙，600萬元以下共58伙。 <br />\n<br />\n對於同期亦有其他新盤推售，她強調不擔心競爭，對本身項目具信心。樓盤1期已售471伙，佔可售單位98%。 <br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，項目第I期去年5月首張價單推出118伙，實用面積304至455方呎，間隔一房至兩房，折實平均呎價15,248元，折實售價498.75萬至730.33萬元。"},{"pid":"f2f120c3c504692acdb5aadc8c38096e777d77ae","tid":1201994,"uid":221051,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"細單位呎價仲貴過一期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6b14c9db473ebcd1cfa33bae0b12eef067a6e4","tid":1201994,"uid":38717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:34:30.000Z","msg":"貴"},{"pid":"41cf1faff91cbb64f3ae199a178be2b536fe4780","tid":1201994,"uid":117435,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2f120c3c504692acdb5aadc8c38096e777d77ae","tid":1201994,"uid":221051,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"細單位呎價仲貴過一期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"上一期好似無開放式？"},{"pid":"4952d75d38b0d6e349032dead4eb320ef193199a","tid":1201994,"uid":221051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41cf1faff91cbb64f3ae199a178be2b536fe4780","tid":1201994,"uid":117435,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2f120c3c504692acdb5aadc8c38096e777d77ae","tid":1201994,"uid":221051,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"細單位呎價仲貴